review_blob: caramel, citrus, resin, brown, hazy, tan foam, medium sweetness, medium bitterness, lightly sour, oily feel, soft carbonation, astringent,
Not horrible, but not one Id go out just to buy. Not much aroma for an IPA. Leaves a bit of a citrusy aftertaste for just a second and then remains sweet.
Looks great in the glass. Small head. Decent aroma, but not huge. Clean on the palate...didnt linger.
